'''Scott Cleverdon''' (born [[July 31]], [[1960s#1969|1969]]) was the voice of [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] and [[Nute Gunray/Legends|Nute Gunray]] in [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace (video game)|''The Phantom Menace'' game]]. He also provided the voice for Kenobi in ''[[Star Wars: Episode I Jedi Power Battles]]''.

